<mvt:item name="html_profile" />
<head>
	<meta charset="utf-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
	<base href="&mvte:global:basehref;">
	<title>Diesel Intercooler Pipes &amp; Charge Pipe Kits | Sinister Diesel</title>
	<meta name="description" content="Shop direct-fit Sinister Diesel intercooler and charge pipe kits for Ford Powerstroke, Chevy Duramax and Ram Cummins trucks. USA-made aluminum construction, secure couplers and fitment-first shopping.">
	<mvt:if expr="g.useDevResources EQ 1"><mvt:item name="head" param="css_list_dev" /><mvt:else><mvt:item name="head" param="css_list" /></mvt:if>
	<mvt:item name="head" param="head_tag" />
</head>
<body class="single-column sd2-seo-landing sd2-charge-pipes-page">
	<mvt:item name="hdft" param="global_header" />
	<mvt:item name="hdft" param="header" />

	<mvt:do name="l.result" file="g.Module_Library_DB" value="Category_Load_Code('954750_intercoolers_pipes_for_powerstroke', l.settings:sd2_cp_powerstroke)" />
	<mvt:do name="l.result" file="g.Module_Library_DB" value="Category_Load_Code('954956_intercoolers_pipes_for_duramax', l.settings:sd2_cp_duramax)" />
	<mvt:do name="l.result" file="g.Module_Library_DB" value="Category_Load_Code('954544_intercoolers_pipes_for_cummins', l.settings:sd2_cp_cummins)" />
	<mvt:do file="g.Module_Feature_URI_UT" name="l.settings:sd2_cp_powerstroke:url" value="Store_Category_URL(l.settings:sd2_cp_powerstroke, NULL)" />
	<mvt:do file="g.Module_Feature_URI_UT" name="l.settings:sd2_cp_duramax:url" value="Store_Category_URL(l.settings:sd2_cp_duramax, NULL)" />
	<mvt:do file="g.Module_Feature_URI_UT" name="l.settings:sd2_cp_cummins:url" value="Store_Category_URL(l.settings:sd2_cp_cummins, NULL)" />

	<main class="sd2-cp">
		<section class="sd2-cp__hero" aria-labelledby="sd2-cp-title">
			<div class="sd2-cp__hero-media" aria-hidden="true">
				<img src="graphics/00000001/7/_DSC4866-Enhanced-SR.webp" alt="" fetchpriority="high">
			</div>
			<div class="sd2-cp__shell sd2-cp__hero-grid">
				<div class="sd2-cp__hero-copy">
					<p class="sd2-cp__eyebrow">Charge-air systems / Made in the USA</p>
					<h1 id="sd2-cp-title">Hold boost.<br>Move air.<br>Stay ready.</h1>
					<p class="sd2-cp__lede">Direct-fit aluminum intercooler and charge pipes engineered to replace failure-prone factory plumbing without turning fitment into guesswork.</p>
					<div class="sd2-cp__actions">
						<a class="sd2-cp__button sd2-cp__button--primary" href="#shop-platform">Shop by truck</a>
						<a class="sd2-cp__button" href="install-part-overviews.html">View part guides</a>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="sd2-cp__hero-console" aria-label="Charge pipe highlights">
					<span class="sd2-cp__console-kicker">System status</span>
					<strong>Boost path<br>reinforced.</strong>
					<div class="sd2-cp__console-data"><span>6061 aluminum</span><span>Direct fit</span><span>No tuning required</span></div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<div class="sd2-cp__signal" aria-label="Product standards">
			<div><span>01</span><strong>Mandrel-bent airflow path</strong></div>
			<div><span>02</span><strong>Heavy-duty silicone boots</strong></div>
			<div><span>03</span><strong>Fitment-first catalog</strong></div>
		</div>

		<section class="sd2-cp__section" id="shop-platform" aria-labelledby="sd2-cp-platform-title">
			<div class="sd2-cp__shell">
				<div class="sd2-cp__section-head">
					<div><p class="sd2-cp__label">Choose your platform</p><h2 id="sd2-cp-platform-title">Start at the engine bay.</h2></div>
					<p>Every route below is connected to its live Miva category, so customers move directly from platform choice to compatible parts.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="sd2-cp__platform-grid">
					<a class="sd2-cp__platform" href="&mvte:sd2_cp_powerstroke:url;">
						<img src="graphics/00000001/7/6.0-BLUE-ENGINE-RGB_2.jpg" alt="Powerstroke engine bay with Sinister Diesel charge pipes" loading="lazy">
						<span class="sd2-cp__platform-number">01 / Ford diesel</span><strong>Powerstroke</strong><span class="sd2-cp__platform-link">View live parts <b>&rarr;</b></span>
					</a>
					<a class="sd2-cp__platform" href="&mvte:sd2_cp_duramax:url;">
						<img src="graphics/00000001/7/2019-ddEngine-2-RGB.jpg" alt="Duramax engine bay with upgraded intercooler piping" loading="lazy">
						<span class="sd2-cp__platform-number">02 / GM diesel</span><strong>Duramax</strong><span class="sd2-cp__platform-link">View live parts <b>&rarr;</b></span>
					</a>
					<a class="sd2-cp__platform" href="&mvte:sd2_cp_cummins:url;">
						<img src="graphics/00000001/7/2019-Cummins-Engine-2-RGB_2.jpg" alt="Cummins engine bay with performance charge-air components" loading="lazy">
						<span class="sd2-cp__platform-number">03 / Ram diesel</span><strong>Cummins</strong><span class="sd2-cp__platform-link">View live parts <b>&rarr;</b></span>
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="sd2-cp__section sd2-cp__section--dark" aria-labelledby="sd2-cp-built-title">
			<div class="sd2-cp__shell sd2-cp__split">
				<div class="sd2-cp__split-media"><img src="graphics/00000001/7/Screenshot 2025-02-21 113231.jpg" alt="Sinister Diesel manufacturing and fabrication" loading="lazy"></div>
				<div class="sd2-cp__split-copy">
					<p class="sd2-cp__label">Designed, made and tested here</p>
					<h2 id="sd2-cp-built-title">Built to replace the weak link.</h2>
					<p>Factory plastic and rubber charge-air components live through heat, pressure and vibration. Sinister Diesel pipes replace that vulnerable path with precisely formed aluminum, durable boots and secure clamps.</p>
					<ul><li>Precision mandrel bends preserve tube diameter.</li><li>Bead-rolled ends help keep couplers seated under load.</li><li>Direct-fit routing follows factory connection points.</li><li>Signature powder coat protects the finished assembly.</li></ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="sd2-cp__section" aria-labelledby="sd2-cp-system-title">
			<div class="sd2-cp__shell">
				<div class="sd2-cp__section-head"><div><p class="sd2-cp__label">Engineer the whole path</p><h2 id="sd2-cp-system-title">Confidence under pressure.</h2></div><p>A charge pipe should improve the ownership experience as much as the engine bay: clear fitment, complete hardware and installation support.</p></div>
				<div class="sd2-cp__feature-grid">
					<article><span>01</span><h3>Stable airflow</h3><p>Smooth, consistent tubing helps reduce the abrupt transitions found in factory charge-air plumbing.</p></article>
					<article><span>02</span><h3>Secure connections</h3><p>Heavy-duty couplers and clamps are selected to stay seated through boost, heat cycles and vibration.</p></article>
					<article><span>03</span><h3>Factory-aware fit</h3><p>Routing is built around the truck's existing turbo, intercooler and intake connection points.</p></article>
					<article><span>04</span><h3>Install support</h3><p>Use the Install Lab for part overviews and practical guidance before the first bolt comes loose.</p></article>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="sd2-cp__section sd2-cp__faq" aria-labelledby="sd2-cp-faq-title">
			<div class="sd2-cp__shell sd2-cp__faq-grid">
				<div><p class="sd2-cp__label">Before you order</p><h2 id="sd2-cp-faq-title">Charge pipe questions, answered.</h2></div>
				<div class="sd2-cp__accordions">
					<details open><summary>Will a charge pipe require tuning?</summary><p>No. These direct-fit charge pipes replace physical charge-air plumbing and are designed to work without ECU recalibration.</p></details>
					<details><summary>How do I find the correct kit?</summary><p>Choose Powerstroke, Duramax or Cummins above, then confirm the model year and engine details shown on the product page against your truck.</p></details>
					<details><summary>What normally comes with a kit?</summary><p>Contents vary by application. Review the live product page for the exact pipe, boots, clamps, seals and application-specific hardware included.</p></details>
					<details><summary>Where can I get installation help?</summary><p>Visit the Install Lab for part overviews or contact Sinister Diesel Parts Tech Support for product-specific guidance.</p></details>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="sd2-cp__final">
			<div class="sd2-cp__shell"><div><p class="sd2-cp__label">Ready to reinforce the system?</p><h2>Choose your truck. Find your pipe.</h2></div><a class="sd2-cp__button sd2-cp__button--light" href="#shop-platform">Shop charge pipes</a></div>
		</section>
	</main>

	<mvt:item name="hdft" param="footer" />
	<mvt:item name="hdft" param="global_footer" />
</body>
</html>
